, "card_id": "Q_298498255", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 360}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "为什么有人说「最好买 80 平米左右的房子」？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-56dab5972f27158c82c6fabbc00406f9_1440w.webp?source=1def8aca"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "58 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/298498255"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8InKyxpMj4+98VEAMaCDI4NjA5NTc2INyljN4FMAA46wZAGnIJMjk4NDk4MjU1eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "27_1775788564.522958", "card_id": "Q_2024877308192854239", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 47}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "现在网文都讲开篇黄金三章，这是否正在扼杀作者的创作力？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "现在不管是网文作者也好，还是网文教程也好，都在强调同一个概念：开篇黄金三章。 前三章必须抛出爽点，埋下钩子，拉满情绪，否则读者划走，编辑也不会过稿。 我也花了大量时间打磨前三章，开头确实变得很炸，有冲突，有悬念，有反转，节奏快得像过山车。但问题是，写到第十章的时候，我发现自己写不下去了。 不是因为没灵感，而是因为我把所有精彩的点子都塞进了前三章，后面的故事反而显得平淡，乏力，像是硬撑着的续命。我开始怀疑这种黄金三章的写法，是不是在逼作者把整本书的精华提前透支？我们是在写一个完整的故事，还是在制造一个三章即巅峰的快消品？ 当所有作者都在追求前三章抓住眼球，会不会导致大家越来越不敢写慢热但有深度的故事？会不会让网文变得千篇一律。 所以我想请教各位有经验的前辈：黄金三章真的是网文创作的铁律吗，它是否在某种程度上扼杀了作者的创作力？ 有没有哪些成功的网文，开篇并不炸，但后劲十足？它们是怎么做到的？"}, "image_area": {"url": ""}, "metrics_area": {"text": "58 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/2024877308192854239"}}, "attached_info": "CkkInKyxpMj4+98VEAMaCTExOTA1NDU4MSDS79LOBjAAOExAG3ITMjAyNDg3NzMwODE5Mjg1NDIzOXgAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "28_1775788564.523945", "card_id": "Q_1943813621542019461", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 79}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "为什么现在路上的 SUV 越来越多？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "观察到一个有趣的趋势：现在路上跑的 SUV 越来越多，从几万块的自主品牌到百万级的豪华车型，SUV 几乎占据了新车市场的大半江山。曾经，轿车是主流，现在却似乎成了「小众」选择。这种现象不仅仅是在中国，全球范围内都有类似的趋势。这背后反映了消费者怎样的需求变化？是空间、实用性、还是更高的驾驶视野带来的心理满足感？想听听大家对于 SUV 热销现象的深层思考。"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/v2-de274fffc61c4b4105d4b5ec7b96359d_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "58 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/1943813621542019461"}}, "attached_info": "CkoInKyxpMj4+98VEAMaCTExNjM1OTYzMSDhnrfFBjAAOIwBQBxyEzE5NDM4MTM2MjE1NDIwMTk0NjF4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "29_1775788564.524494", "card_id": "Q_1980647393792893898", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 67}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "孩子让反复读一本书，家长该如何应对？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "幼儿园小班的孩子，一本书反复读，读完一遍再讲一遍，你们遇到这种情况都怎么做的？"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/v2-bb2141241b102b812c3b21f167a25c04_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "58 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/1980647393792893898"}}, "attached_info": "CkkInKyxpMj4+98VEAMaCTExNzYxMTkxNCCBn8/JBjAAOE9AHXITMTk4MDY0NzM5Mzc5Mjg5Mzg5OHgAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}], "paging": {"is_end": true, "is_start": false, "next": "", "previous": "", "totals": 0}, "fresh_text": "热榜已更新", "display_num": 15, "display_first": true, "fb_bill_main_rise": 0, "head_zone": {"type": "billboard_lantern", "data": [{"id": "2025870898888975635", "link_url": "https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/2025869502819084192?share_code=gtVMg5YTfrO6&utm_psn=2025870520957052604", "title": "网警打掉利用 「外挂」抢票的犯罪团伙", "source_type": 0, "attached_info": "Ci4QABoTMjAyNTg3MDg5ODg4ODk3NTYzNXITMjAyNTg3MDg5ODg4ODk3NTYzNXgA", "tag": "关注", "tag_bg_color": "GRD01A"}, {"id": "1989780245977532317", "link_url": "https://www.zhihu.com/appview/community_construction", "title": "辟谣专区", "source_type":